com.ibm.ecm.api.coresdk.model

Interface IBMECMUserRole

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<IBMECMBaseObject>, IBMECMBaseObject, Serializable

    public interface IBMECMUserRole
extends IBMECMBaseObject
    Represents a role that users or groups can be assigned to. A role is a collection of access rights that can be assigned to a user or group that enable it to carry out certain tasks.
